<i> that I almost fell</i>
<i> in the hallway.</i>

17:08.598 --> 17:11.699
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

17:11.734 --> 17:12.967
<i> And all of a sudden,</i>

17:13.002 --> 17:15.636
I hear these phones
ringing again.

17:15.672 --> 17:20.007
<i> [phones ringing]</i>

17:20.043 --> 17:22.910
Like every phone in the hospital
was going off at the same time.

17:22.946 --> 17:27.348
<i> [phones ringing]</i>

17:27.383 --> 17:30.084
- [growling]

17:30.119 --> 17:37.091
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

17:37.126 --> 17:40.061
- My head was just slammed back
against the wall,

17:40.096 --> 17:43.364
<i> so hard that it almost</i>
<i> knocked me out.</i>

17:43.399 --> 17:46.367
<i> [high-pitched whine]</i>

17:46.402 --> 17:52.540
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

17:52.575 --> 17:55.142
<i> I realized then</i>

17:55.178 --> 17:57.378
that I needed to get some help.

18:05.021 --> 18:08.055
<i> [haunting music]</i>
.

18:08.091 --> 18:15.029
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

18:18.201 --> 18:19.767
[phone rings]

18:19.802 --> 18:22.203
-<i> One evening, my phone rings.</i>

18:22.238 --> 18:23.871
- Hello?
